  "content": "<p data-pid=\"Rr331-yr\">如果需要调整正反面，就得通过改变笔记类型。</p><p data-pid=\"OqsDcdvT\">要调整一个牌组的正反面，就要只选中一个牌组的所有卡片</p><p data-pid=\"2pajDIyd\">方法如下：</p><p data-pid=\"2EnsBWZ5\">先点击你要修改的牌组，然后 ctrl + a 选中所有卡片</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f9548ca10e818bb78f64547bebfab4d7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"847\" data-rawheight=\"699\" data-original-token=\"v2-0e24cdb971eae93dc36435891ad24c29\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b90a0385aaa3fd27e5849be8bcaa83e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"847\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f9548ca10e818bb78f64547bebfab4d7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;847&#39; height=&#39;699&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"847\" data-rawheight=\"699\" data-original-token=\"v2-0e24cdb971eae93dc36435891ad24c29\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b90a0385aaa3fd27e5849be8bcaa83e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"847\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f9548ca10e818bb78f64547bebfab4d7_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f9548ca10e818bb78f64547bebfab4d7_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"z8Ct-NAx\">点击笔记-&gt;改变笔记类型</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-35ee707dde0aea633204bda7736d0653_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"399\" data-rawheight=\"470\" data-original-token=\"v2-54d7311c01c2c8045f3bee4a6d73015f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ea6ccfd96ef1b88ed64cb3b90ab4a603_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"399\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xm